   313вҶ’	/**
   314вҶ’	HTTP method used to make the request.
   315вҶ’
   316вҶ’	Internally, the standard methods (`GET`, `POST`, `PUT`, `PATCH`, `HEAD` and `DELETE`) are uppercased in order to avoid server errors due to case sensitivity.
   317вҶ’	*/
